*virt-manager-0.4.0 (10 Jun 2007)

  10 Jun 2007; Donnie Berkholz <dberkholz@gentoo.org>; +metadata.xml,
  +virt-manager-0.4.0.ebuild:
  Add a graphical tool for administering virtual machines including Xen, QEMU
  and KVM.

